com.software.reuze

Interface gb_i_OctreeVisitor


  • public interface gb_i_OctreeVisitor
    This interface is the core part of the visitor pattern application for gb_PointOctrees. It can be used to apply a procedure to all tree nodes when passed to gb_PointOctree#applyVisitor(OctreeVisitor).
